{
    "$schema": "schema://living-narrative-engine/expression.schema.json",
    "id": "emotions-admiration:admiration_swell",
    "description": "Admiration swell—respect rises and steadies into a quiet uplift. Attention tightens into appreciation; the mind starts framing what it sees as exemplary or worth emulating. It can feel cleanly inspiring or slightly humbling without tipping into shame.",
